            {
                id = "0", speaker = "A Furious Girl in a Niche",
                text = "*(In a niche of the Wall, a young woman flickers — translucent at the edges, fading, *going* — but her eyes are fierce and entirely present, and when she sees you she does not reach out in hope like the others. She *glares.*)* No. *(flatly.)* Whatever you're here for — *no.* I know that look. I've had a hundred of you come down the line with that *exact* look. You're here to *save* me. You've heard of me — *Aldric's daughter, the merchant's lost girl, fading in the dark* — and you've come to make me into the thing that makes *you* feel like a hero. *(she folds fading arms.)* I would rather *finish going out* than be one more person's *reason.* So unless you've got something better than *rescue*, keep walking.",
