                text = "*(She stares — and for the first time the fury cracks to show what it's been *guarding*: a terror of hoping.)* A road out. *(unsteadily.)* Don't. Don't *do* that to me. Do you know how many times I've talked myself *out* of hope down here? It's the only mercy the niche offers — once you stop hoping, the fading stops *hurting.* And you walk up and say *road out* and undo *months* of — *(she stops, jaw set.)* ...Furious and alive, you said. Not nobly gone. *(a flickering, dangerous spark.)* You don't want to *rescue* me. You want to *recruit* me. That's — that's *different.* A rescue makes me cargo. A recruitment means you think I'm still *good for something* besides being grieved. *(the fury reignites, but pointed *outward* now, toward the Wall, toward the road.)* Then *yes.* Yes, gods damn you and your hope — *yes.* But understand: I don't come up there to be your *redemption arc.* I come up to be *furious in person*, at the *thing that did this*, with my *own two restored hands.* You're not saving a reason, Returned. You're *arming* one. Get me out of this niche and point me at the Wall.",
                autoNextNodeId = "close",
                onEnter = new[] { new FlagClause { key = "npc.maerin_recruit", op = FlagOp.SetTrue }, new FlagClause { key = "sq.maerin_recruit", op = FlagOp.SetTrue }, new FlagClause { key = "act2.maerin_will_return", op = FlagOp.SetTrue }, new FlagClause { key = "companion.maerin.approval", op = FlagOp.AddInt, amount = 5 } },
