                text = "*(Her edges flare, affronted.)* Don't *read* me. *(sharp.)* I didn't ask to be *understood*, I asked to be *left.* You think naming my fear *defuses* it? It just means now *you* know where to *press.* *(she turns half away, flickering.)* Go be perceptive at someone who *wants* saving. I'll do my fading *unflattened*, thank you, and *spite* will keep the corners on just fine without your *help.* *(but she doesn't tell you to leave — quite — and the glare she gives you has a question buried in it she won't ask aloud.)*",
